{"tid":1562330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[55000] 支爆煙花、應該和誰看。","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T23:35:08.000Z","uid":20723,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c21595e625c3383d445ad78eeca90bea5e25fb62","tid":1562330,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YxUaVpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxUaVpQ.jpg&h=d4b38d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支爆應該和誰看</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=3fe5c5c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記得Check verify email</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊係侵侵啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903500204641b1d4f92c6a8eb9aec5e64b4ac399","tid":1562330,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"